---
title: Sweet-Soy Veggie Mince & Udon Noodle Stir-Fry with Plum Sauce & Parsley
description: Soothing noodles are wrapping up all the flavours of sweet and soy plant-based mince to transform into a vibrant stir-fry. You don’t want to miss the sweetened notes of plum sauce beside a rich stir-fry sauce - this bowl is going to be a veggie fan-fav for sure.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
